# SIGNAL Token Service — Environment Variables
#
# DO NOT commit a copy of this file with real values.
# Use `npx wrangler secret put GEMINI_API_KEY` to set the secret in Cloudflare.
# For local dev with `wrangler dev`, create a .dev.vars file (also git-ignored) with:

GEMINI_API_KEY=your_google_ai_studio_api_key_here
